OL,3,CYorkshire councils spend #30,000
OL,4,Cremoving flags
OL,6,FA Yorkshire council has spent more
OL,7,Fthan #16,000 removing national flags
OL,8,Ffrom a city's streets after saying
OL,9,Fthey had left some residents "feeling
OL,10,Fthreatened and uncomfortable".
OL,12,FFigures obtained through a freedom of
OL,13,Finformation request show the cost of
OL,14,Ftaking unauthorised Union and St
OL,15,FGeorge's Cross flags down from
OL,16,Flampposts and other public places in
OL,17,FYork had cost the Labour-run city
OL,18,Fcouncil #16,378.
