OL,3,CYorkshire councils spend #30,000
OL,4,Cremoving flags
OL,6,FIt comes after the council said the
OL,7,Fincrease in "flag flying" had
OL,8,Fcoincided with a rise in racist
OL,9,Fincidents, including children being
OL,10,Fabused on their way to school.
OL,12,FIn a statement in September the
OL,13,Fcouncil said it would take flags down
OL,14,Fto avoid causing division.
OL,16,F"Many in our communities are feeling
OL,17,Fthreatened and uncomfortable," it said.
