OL,3,CYorkshire councils spend #30,000
OL,4,Cremoving flags
OL,6,F"Children have been racially abused by
OL,7,Fadults on their way to school and
OL,8,Fcouncil staff are being abused simply
OL,9,Ffor doing their jobs of removing
OL,10,Fgraffiti from our roads. This cannot
OL,11,Fgo on."
OL,13,FElsewhere in Yorkshire Barnsley
OL,14,FCouncil, which is also Labour-
OL,15,Fcontrolled, has spent about #6,000
OL,16,Fremoving flags. It has previously said
OL,17,Fit would remove flags considered to
OL,18,Fpose a safety risk.
