OL,6,FDoncaster Council spent #1,071 on
OL,7,Fstaff time and machinery. It said the
OL,8,Fcost related only to the removal of
OL,9,Fgraffiti from roundabouts and zebra
OL,10,Fcrossings, not flying flags.
OL,12,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council said
OL,13,Fit had spent more than #6,000
OL,14,F"restoring markings on the highway
OL,15,Fbecause of the painting of
OL,16,Funauthorised red crosses".
