OL,3,CYorkshire councils spend #30,000
OL,4,Cremoving flags
OL,6,FA spokesperson said the council was
OL,7,F"committed to removing any unsafe or
OL,8,Funauthorised displays, paintings, or
OL,9,Fgraffiti that could distract or
OL,10,Fconfuse drivers".
OL,12,FThey added: "When reports have been
OL,13,Freceived about such displays on public
OL,14,Fhighways, the council has investigated
OL,15,Fand removed them where necessary to
OL,16,Fensure the safety of all road users.
OL,18,F"Any council-owned infrastructure that
OL,19,Fis vandalised will be reported to
OL,20,FHumberside Police as criminal damage."
