OL,6,FOther councils in the Calendar region
OL,7,Fdid not respond to the request.
OL,9,FThe data was obtained by political
OL,10,Fadvisor Pablo O'Hana, who submitted
OL,11,Frequests to more than 380 local
OL,12,Fauthorities across the country.
OL,14,FHe said: "It worries me a lot that
OL,15,Fthis flag is being cheapened and taken
OL,16,Fas a way to divide our communities and
OL,17,Fhurt our country.
